title: CM GB calls on PM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Dec 27 (APP): Chief Minister Gilgit Baltistan Khalid Khursheed Monday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan.
During the meeting, reforms process over revenue sector and ongoing uplift projects under Public Sector Development Programme (PSDP) in Gilgit Baltistan were discussed.
Besides, the steps taken to ensure uninterrupted supply of wheat were also discussed.
